### 创建物品（属于家庭 @fid）
POST http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "大米",
  "unit": "袋",
  "quantity": 5,
  "location": "厨房角落",
  "owner_id": 1,
  "notes": "10kg 袋装东北大米",
  "raw_input": "补充5袋大米",
  "check_interval_days": 60,
  "tags": [1, 2]
}

###

### 获取该家庭下所有物品（支持标签筛选）
GET http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 获取需要检查的物品（基于 check_interval_days）
GET http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items/check-needed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 单个物品标记为已检查（物品 id = 1）
PATCH http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items/1/check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 批量标记物品为已检查
PATCH http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items/bulk-check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemList": ["1", "2"]
}

###

### 批量为物品添加标签
PATCH http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items/bulk-add-tags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemList": ["1", "2"],
  "tagList": [3, 4]
}

###

### 更新某个物品的信息
PUT http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "更新为红烧味",
  "quantity": 8,
  "tags": [3]
}

###

### 删除某个物品（逻辑删除）
DELETE http://localhost:8000/families/{{fid}}/items/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

